headline: Healthcare Sector Taps AI Boom via Intuitive Surgical Stock (ISRG)
summary: When investors think of artificial intelligence (AI), names like Nvidia (NVDA), Palantir (PLTR), and Alphabet (GOOGL) typically come to mind. But AI’s impact extends well beyond the traditional tech sector. A standout example is Intuitive Surgical (ISRG), the clear global leader in robotic surgery, now making significant strides in integrating AI into healthcare.
